msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.57:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "6. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 57. Paṭhamamahāsamuddasutta → samuddasuttaṃ (bj) | samudda 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.57:0.3"
msgid "57. Paṭhamamahāsamuddasutta"
msgstr "57. The Ocean (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.463"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso mahāsamuddato dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni "
"uddharitāni."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a man was to draw up two or three drops of water from "
"the ocean."

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni, yaṃ "
"vā mahāsamudde udakan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the two or three drops drawn out or the water in the ocean?”"

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—mahāsamudde udakaṃ; appamattakāni dve "
"vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the water in the ocean is certainly more. The two or three drops drawn "
"out are tiny."

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.5"
msgid ""
"Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti "
"mahāsamudde udakaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the water in the ocean, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s "
"not even a fraction.”"

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe …"
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple …"

msgctxt "sn56.57:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.57:1.8"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
